<i>noun</i>: 위안 [위안], 위로 [위로] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>위안 [위안]</dt><br>
<dd>comfot; consolation; solace</dd><br>
<dd>위로하여 마음을 편하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of soothing someone and easing his/her mind.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>위로 [위로]</dt><br>
<dd>consolation; comfort</dd><br>
<dd>따뜻한 말이나 행동 등으로 괴로움을 덜어 주거나 슬픔을 달래 줌.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of easing someone's pain or sadness through warm words or behavior, etc.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>